'''Beyond Bree 1991 J.R.R. Tolkien Calendar''' was produced by the [[American Mensa Tolkien Special Interest Group]] and edited by [[Carl F. Hostetter]]. The calendar contains black and white illustrations by an international list of nine artists.

{{Beyond Bree (calendar)nav| 1989 J.R.R. Tolkien Calendar| J.R.R. Tolkien Calendar 1992}}

* Dimensions: 11 x 8.5 inches
* Stapled on the fold
* Punched hanging hole
* Envelope
